<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>Status Update Notification</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div style="font-family: sans-serif;">
    <img src="https://openeu.csee.tech/project-europe-no-bg.png" alt="Project Europe Logo" style="height: 50px;" />
    <h2>Hello {{ recipient }},</h2>
    <p>The status of a legislation you’re following has changed:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Title:</strong> {{ title }}</li>
      <li><strong>Old status:</strong> {{ old_status }}</li>
      <li><strong>New status:</strong> {{ new_status }}</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can view it <a href="{{ link }}">here</a>.</p>
    <p>— The OpenEU Team</p>
    <footer style="font-size: 0.8em; color: #666;">&copy; {{ current_year }} OpenEU GmbH</footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
